title: 801. Top & Surprise Prospect at Each Position
itunes:title: 801. Top & Surprise Prospect at Each Position
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. Throughout the episode, the guys break down the top prospect at each position. The pair also discuss a surprise prospect at every position group.

Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
